
# Hero Images Directory

This directory contains hero slider background images.

## Image Guidelines:
- Recommended size: 1920x1080px (16:9 aspect ratio)
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Quality: High resolution for crisp display
- File naming: Use descriptive names like 'lab-equipment.jpg', 'research-facility.jpg'

## Current Images:
- slide-1-precision.jpg - Laboratory equipment showcase
- slide-2-research.jpg - Advanced research facility
- slide-3-future.jpg - Innovation workspace

## How to Add New Images:
1. Upload your image files to this directory
2. Update the image paths in src/data/heroContent.ts
3. Update the alt text for accessibility

